  "title": "Fish Cutter",
  "description": "<p>Working Hours:<br>\nTuesday to Sunday, 3:30 AM – 12:30 PM<br>\n<br>\nRest Day:<br>\nEvery Monday (4 days off per month)<br>\n<br>\nLocation:<br>\nBuona Vista, Singapore<br>\n<br>\nJob Description:<br>\nWe are a seafood retail company operating in a wet market, looking for a skilled Fish Cutter to join our team.<br>\n<br>\nResponsibilities:<br>\n<br>\nCutting and preparing fish and seafood for sale<br>\n<br>\nMaintaining cleanliness and hygiene in the stall<br>\n<br>\nEnsuring proper handling and storage of seafood products<br>\n<br>\nWorking efficiently in a fast-paced market environment<br>\n<br>\nRequirements:<br>\n<br>\nMust be able to work 6 days a week, including weekends and public holidays<br>\n<br>\nExperience in fish cutting preferred<br>\n<br>\nResponsible, punctual, and able to work independently<br>\n<br>\nround trip from SG to malaysia is allow<br>\n<br>\nLEE LAI MUN R1657696</p>",
